name: Vepian Ultimatum
description: My first attempt at pen. A mix between some custom finetuned models and a merge of Deliberate and Protogen with some other models. (Main formula is CM+(D-P)*0.5+OM, where CM - Custom Models, D - Delibirate v2, P - Protogen x3.4 photorealism, OM - other models). Not really sure if it's good, just give me and my creation a chance.
